This combination delivers a warm, smoky, and slightly peppery profile that s both satisfying and versatile. Whether you re preparing a hearty breakfast, a quick lunch, or a comforting dinner, Carmela Chicken Sausage and Bouillon adds depth and flavor with minimal effort. The product s ingredients reflect a balance between flavor and shelf stability: mechanically separated chicken, water, salt, corn syrup solids, dextrose, hydrolyzed corn, torula and brewer s yeast, wheat gluten, soy protein, sugar, modified corn starch, onion powder, garlic powder, spices, disodium inosinate, disodium guanylate, chili pepper, natural smoke flavor, natural flavorings, sodium erythorbate, and sodium nitrite. While it contains common allergens like soy and wheat, it s free from artificial preservatives and designed to maintain its quality over time.
